author: David Raleigh
title: ‘Everyone still thinks it’s a joke’ - parents of toddler with coronavirus speak out
description: Jayce Lyons (2 1/2) ‘up and about, but he’s still coughing’
content:
The parents of a two-and-half-year-old boy who tested positive for COVID-19, warned people to heed expert medical advice about the virus and stay indoors to stop it spreading.
